Team: Daiana, Jovani, Julian

Task: Develop an unplugged activity for a CS concept that has been covered this summer. Describe your concept and activity

Concepts: Random numbers and conditionals

Task description:
2 dice rolling, number of rounds: 2 per player ( if you donâ€™t have Craps)

Players: 1
Roll 2 dice

If:
2 OR 7 -Craps. You lose.
Else:
            Roll the dice again
             If
                    Roll the same number  you win
             Else
         7 you lose


Students will be tasked to create their own game that includes 1-2 players, 2 dice, and conditionals similar to the example.

Differentiation:
Mild: Create a simple game that involves one of either IF or ELSE.
Medium: Create a game that involves both IF and ELSE.
Spicy: Modify the game of Craps that involves at least 2 nested IF or ELSE statements.

Scaffolding: Worksheet to help students develop game includes:
Rules
Materials needed
IF ELSE sentence starters.
Number of players.
